WEBVTT

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:31.949
a leading expert on how people manage
the boundary between work and life.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:34.896
Nancy finds that unhappy workaholics

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:38.120
have higher risk for cardiovascular
disease and diabetes.

00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:41.496
But she discovered
another kind of workaholic --

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:43.416
an engaged workaholic.

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:48.256
NR: People who do feel compulsion

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:50.616
and some guilt when they're not working

00:04:50.640 --> 00:04:53.616
but who also absolutely love their jobs.

00:04:53.640 --> 00:04:57.056
Who are engaged in it,
who are passionate about it,

00:04:57.080 --> 00:04:59.416
who find meaning in their jobs.

